    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0ed",
      "text": "WidthにScaleが影響する罠",
      "created": 1529462719,
      "updated": 1529465457,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0ee",
      "text": "[Rect Transform]のPosにはScaleが影響しないが、WidthにはScaleが影響する",
      "created": 1529465361,
      "updated": 1529465392,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0ef",
      "text": " これに気付いていないと予期せず小さすぎるWidth, Heightを指定してしまう",
      "created": 1529465414,
      "updated": 1529465432,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
