    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0f7",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/cc843c01d1dd77c77095389ad28b1981]",
      "created": 1529463048,
      "updated": 1529463048,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0f8",
      "text": "\t[モノリス]の上端を基準点にして、そこからY方向-1の点にテキストの上端を合わせている",
      "created": 1529462723,
      "updated": 1529464144,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0f9",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1529463298,
      "updated": 1529463298,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0fa",
      "text": " Widthはいま0だけど、Truncateする場合には適切に(この場合は4とかに)するべき？",
      "created": 1529463471,
      "updated": 1529463981,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0fb",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/fc001ca30c37b1577bdc2a6153ce217d]",
      "created": 1529463473,
      "updated": 1529463476,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0fc",
      "text": "\t\tTruncateしてないとこうなる",
      "created": 1529463476,
      "updated": 1529463486,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0fd",
      "text": "  と思ったがそもそも水平方向のTruncateはなかった",
      "created": 1529463984,
      "updated": 1529463992,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0fe",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1529463725,
      "updated": 1529463725,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a0ff",
      "text": " >[Alignment]の上下方向のボタンを、PowerPointなどの上ぞろえ下ぞろえと混同した。",
      "created": 1529463922,
      "updated": 1529463925,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a100",
      "text": "  >これは基準点に対してテキストの上端でそろえるか下端でそろえるかという意味なので、アイコン上での表現と逆に「下端でそろえる」をした方がテキストは上に行く。",
      "created": 1529463922,
      "updated": 1529463927,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a101",
      "text": "\tと思ったが違うみたい",
      "created": 1529463486,
      "updated": 1529463728,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a102",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/7b9985546531023cf170b8a4a99ca6c1]",
      "created": 1529463728,
      "updated": 1529463733,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a103",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/7a3f200a666ff715451808bc2f2b74a2]",
      "created": 1529463730,
      "updated": 1529463759,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a104",
      "text": "\t\tPosにはScaleが影響しないが、WidthにはScaleが影響するみたいだ",
      "created": 1529463759,
      "updated": 1529463795,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a105",
      "text": "  \t今までそれを誤解していて想定より小さく作られていた",
      "created": 1529463797,
      "updated": 1529463816,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a106",
      "text": "   この状況でなら下ぞろえでモノリス下端に張り付く",
      "created": 1529463816,
      "updated": 1529463902,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a107",
      "text": "   縦幅が想定より小さかったために基準点に対するアライメントに見えていた",
      "created": 1529463892,
      "updated": 1529463946,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a108",
      "text": "\t\tモノリス中心を基準点にしたうえでPosは0でもよい",
      "created": 1529463484,
      "updated": 1529464136,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a109",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1529464824,
      "updated": 1529464824,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d726aff09e000076a10a",
      "text": "\tWrapとTruncateを設定するとこうなる",
      "created": 1529464824,
      "updated": 1529464831,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
